snippet.title: Fashion Police Squad Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: http://steam.fashionpolicesquad.com/

Fashion Police Squad is a humorous Retro FPS where you fight against fashion crime using fabulous attire enhancing weaponry!
